                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[21.08.2007]</p>
                <p>30 journalists from all over the world to visit the Svalbard Global Seed Vault on Wednesday. The Svalbard Global Seed Vault (SGS) is taking shape. Construction work started in April 2007 and the first blastings were performed in May. The facility will be opened on 28 February 2008.  </p>
                
                
